                        <td>Cartas consideradas: Æmberlution, Ammonia Clouds, Axiom of Grist, Ballcano, Champion’s Challenge, Coward’s End, Crushing Charge, Earthshaker, Gateway to Dis, General Sherman, Grand Alliance Council, Groundbreaking Discovery, Harbinger of Doom, Key to Dis, Kiligog's Trench, Krrrzzzaaap, Mind Bullets, Mælstrom, Numquid the Fair, Onyx Knight, Opal Knight, Ragnarok, Red Alert, Savage Clash, Skixuno, Spartasaur, Strange Gizmo, The Big One, The Spirit’s Way, Unlocked Gateway, Unnatural Selection</td>
